<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">秋风起，秋意浓</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">600岁的紫禁城迎来又一个秋天</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">红墙黄瓦，木叶萧萧</span></strong></span></p>
